{"tid":2234650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角皇都戲院強拍 新世界底價47.76億投得","createTime":"2020-10-08T05:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:34:58.000Z","uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7ae9f5a9ebf207e79dbe30ecd25fe6be435476","tid":2234650,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:04:23.000Z","msg":"古蹟重建｜北角皇都戲院強拍 新世界底價47.76億投得 測量師：保育發展難計投資額<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201008/COTXF6ME6FACZCIP7QVJ2JC4HY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201008%2FCOTXF6ME6FACZCIP7QVJ2JC4HY%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5AAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=cad97fa7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201008%2FCOTXF6ME6FACZCIP7QVJ2JC4HY%2F&h=024ed31d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201008/COTXF6ME6FACZCIP7QVJ2JC4HY/</a><br />\n<br />\n歷來最大宗強拍項目，位於北角英皇道之北、渣華道之南及與電照街交界，部份建築獲古諮會評為一級歷史建築物的皇都戲院，今日公開拍賣出售，底價47.76億元，強拍申請發展商為新世界發展（017），最終亦由新世界以底價投得。"},{"pid":"93d1394c7020b986b5bce78e8385d4efbb48fba9","tid":2234650,"uid":155674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"上次有一次夜晚經過 <br />\n見到勁多老鼠喺附近<br />\n所以真係要處理一下皇都<br />\n就算唔拆都一定要搞搞呢個地方 <br />\n如果唔係嘅話 對附近居民好唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7aaa4da52d1d7a68495b2bffd9c7384acd53e4","tid":2234650,"uid":7179,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"𠴱個位真係要搞搞佢<br />\n次次行經都會一陣味 入到去又殘又舊<br />\n而且個戲院係一級歷史建築 我諗都會做好保育先再起其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e196af0231bcf195a8e1780942ecfc39727a1f","tid":2234650,"uid":342595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"佢老細鄭生咁鐘意藝術品<br />